column5: I didnt get a chance to do any fishing today cuz i promised my dad i was going to take him to the car show. I got some pics taken and before i post them i just want to make sure that its ok to post them here since they are not really fishing related  Ty for your time
I'm not a mod, but I highly doubt there would be a problem with it. Just put "NF" at the end of your post title (non fishing).
Post them already enough car guys here to enjoy them for sure.
Car guy here.... I manage a parts store.... c'mon post the pics..
